\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was expected to defend her championship at the 2022 Red Bull BC One World Final in New York, but was beat out in the intense final round by India Dewi (b-girl India) from the Netherlands before dominating in the Olympic Qualifier Series in Budapest in June.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1273, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1068, \"end\": 1083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Bull_BC_One\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Red Bull BC One\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Bull_BC_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Bull_BC_One\"}, {\"begin\": 1084, \"end\": 1095, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Bull_BC_One\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.28653293553649e-14, \"text\": \"World Final\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Bull_BC_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Bull_BC_One\"}, {\"begin\": 1099, \"end\": 1107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999983924681, \"rank\": 1.0306855458090552e-09, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 1156, \"end\": 1161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7050495575821494, \"rank\": 0.40712958784332726, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1175, \"end\": 1180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7050495575821494, \"rank\": 0.40712958784332726, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1191, \"end\": 1202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6002690227995778, \"rank\": 0.6142237593756595, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1256, \"end\": 1264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999962528254122, \"rank\": 3.745653032969245e-06, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her championship\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1055}, {\"ngram\": \"the intense final round\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1152}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Qualifier Series\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1252}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With all the anticipation around breaking officially debuting as an Olympic sport, Edra and her teammates are navigating the pressure that comes with performing a uniquely American artform while facing tough competition from what has now become a global phenomenon.\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1447, \"end\": 1455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999987462700702, \"rank\": 8.193673538549136e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the anticipation\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1300}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic sport\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1356}, {\"ngram\": \"Edra\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1362}, {\"ngram\": \"her teammates\", \"from\":